text: Nika Stanović (born 2 October 1993) is a Croatian volleyball player. She plays as outside hitter for Croatian club ŽOK Kaštela. ==References== ==External links== *Nika Stanović at CEV.eu Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Croatian women's volleyball players Category:Sportspeople from Dubrovnik
